title: Hurricane Delta Steals the Spotlight
description:
Wendi Nix, Todd McShay, and Desmond Howard discuss the results that could come from Hurricane Delta, Saturday's Miami v Clemson game, and Trey Lance declaring for the 2021 NFL Draft. Wendi also talks to Georgia Head Coach Kirby Smart about this weekend's matchup against Tennessee.
